{"ja288:0.1":"Jataka ","ja288:0.2":"Tikanipata ","ja288:0.3":"Abbhantaravagga ","ja288:0.4":"8. Macchuddanajataka ","ja288:1.1":"“Agghanti maccha adhikam sahassam, ","ja288:1.2":"Na so atthi yo imam saddaheyya; ","ja288:1.3":"Mayhanca assu idha satta masa, ","ja288:1.4":"Ahampi tam macchuddanam kineyyam”. ","ja288:2.1":"“Macchanam bhojanam datva, ","ja288:2.2":"mama dakkhinamadisi; ","ja288:2.3":"Tam dakkhinam sarantiya, ","ja288:2.4":"katam apacitim taya”. ","ja288:3.1":"“Padutthacittassa na phati hoti, ","ja288:3.2":"Na capi tam devata pujayanti; ","ja288:3.3":"Yo bhataram pettikam sapateyyam, ","ja288:3.4":"Avancayi dukkatakammakari”ti. ","ja288:4.1":"Macchuddanajatakam atthamam. "}